This paper deals with the computation of approximate solutions to a non-commutative generalization of the approximate GCD problem, which is a problem in symbolic computation. The paper uses techniques from numerical linear algebra and differential algebra. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.SC (Symbolic Computation), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DS (Dynamical Systems). The paper also involves numerical methods, so cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is a likely sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with algorithms and complexity, so cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possible sub-category.
